ung love.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Apr 2020) 0aFrench fictionx20th century. 0aMan-woman relationshipsxFiction. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aPolizzotti, Mark40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300218916423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300218916.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aEBA_FAO